description: This high-performance charger delivers 240W of power, allowing powerful gaming laptops to charge at warp speed. It is equipped with over voltage and over current protection to ensure safe and reliable charging. Despite its powerful capabilities, the charger is compact and portable, making it easy to carry and use anywhere.

name: ASUS AC65-00 65W USB Type-C Laptop Adapter
shortDescription: This compact and portable charger features a USB Type-C connector with USB PD 3.0 technology and multiple output protection.
description: Designed for convenience, this charger boasts a compact and portable design, making it easy to carry anywhere. It comes equipped with a USB Type-C connector and utilizes USB Power Delivery (PD) 3.0 technology for efficient and fast charging. The charger also includes multiple output protection features, ensuring safe and reliable charging for your devices.

name: Foldable Laptop Stand
shortDescription: Compatible with laptops from 8 to 17.3 inches, this stand offers height adjustment from 46.5 to 136.5mm. Dimensions when unfolded: 270 x 235.6 x 136.5 mm; dimensions before folding: 270 x 55 x 136.5 mm.
description: This versatile laptop stand is compatible with laptops ranging from 8 to 17.3 inches, providing a flexible solution for various devices. It features adjustable height settings from 46.5 to 136.5mm, allowing for ergonomic positioning. When unfolded, the stand measures 270 x 235.6 x 136.5 mm, and when folded, it compacts down to 270 x 55 x 136.5 mm, making it easy to store and transport.

name: UGREEN LP230 (80348)
shortDescription: Suitable for 11-17 inch laptops, this stand offers adjustable height from 87 to 131mm. It features a stable structure with a 20kg bearing capacity and is made from stainless steel, silicone, PC, and ABS.
description: Designed for 11-17 inch laptops, this stand provides an adjustable height range of 87 to 131mm, allowing for ergonomic use. It boasts a stable structure capable of bearing up to 20kg. Constructed from high-quality materials including stainless steel, silicone, PC, and ABS, this stand ensures durability and stability for long-term use.

name: ASUS ROG Archer Backpack BP1505
shortDescription: Featuring a modular compartment design, this lightweight bag is water-repellent for added protection.
description: This versatile bag is designed with a modular compartment system, allowing for easy organization and customization of your storage space. It is water-repellent, providing protection against the elements, and lightweight, ensuring comfortable portability for daily use.

name: ASUS AP4600 Professional Backpack
shortDescription: Featuring over a dozen specially designed pockets for quick access, this slim and lightweight bag offers a water-repellent and scratch-resistant finish with a breathable shoulder harness for everyday cooling comfort.
description: This practical and stylish bag is equipped with over a dozen specially designed pockets, providing quick and easy access to your essentials on the go. It features a water-repellent and scratch-resistant finish, ensuring durability and protection for everyday use. The slim and lightweight design, combined with a breathable shoulder harness, offers enhanced comfort and cooling, making it ideal for daily carry.

name: UGREEN CM359 (80551)
shortDescription: Enhance productivity and declutter your workspace with the UGREEN CM359 Black Laptop Stand, a sleek 5-in-1 docking station that elevates your laptop to an ergonomic height.
description: Enhance your productivity and declutter your workspace with the UGREEN CM359 (80551) Black Laptop Stand. This sleek and versatile stand doubles as a 5-in-1 docking station, providing you with multiple connectivity options. Elevate your laptop to an ergonomic height, reducing strain on your neck and wrists. With its modern design and sturdy construction, the UGREEN CM359 is the perfect accessory for any home or office setup. Get ready to work smarter and streamline your workflow with this all-in-one laptop stand and docking station.
